data.description: Beautifully updated home with vinyl wood floors, paint, granite, and more!  This four bedroom home is within walking distance to Lamar HS and has excellent access to I30 from Cooper Street and Fielder Road.  Butler Elem is the primary school.  Replaced items over five years are water heater, ceiling fans, roof, gutters, exterior paint, fence repair and replacement, removal in inground pool, and updated baths.  This home has all the alure of a new home and the charm of custom home.  Beautiful wood cabinets in the spacious kitchen complete with island work space.  You can be Home for Christmas if you act now.  Help Santa complete your Christmas dreams.
